# Do not send multi‑GB data to the Docker daemon (saves disk/RAM at COPY and unpack).
# Keep these bind-mounted or synced on the instance; mini config still needs these paths at runtime.
local_retriever/corpus
local_retriever/indexes
local_retriever/models
# In case a huge file lives at repo root by mistake
**/wiki18_100w.jsonl

# Hybrid image:
#   - retriever + evaluation_search_r1 source IS COPY'd (baked in).
#   - training/ is NOT copied — repo cloned on Vast at runtime; image only
#     ships uv + a pre-warmed wheel cache for NeMo-RL. So exclude the heavy
#     training/nemo_rl/ source from the build context to keep builds fast.
training/nemo_rl
training/.venv
docs
data
data_subsample
.git
